media:group.media:title: LAFC vs. Philadelphia Union | MLS Cup Highlights | ESPN FC
media:group.media:description:
LAFC win the MLS Cup against Philadelphia Union, 3-3 (3-0, on penalties. Gareth Bale scored late in stoppage time to send the game to penalties.
